      <title>YPF 计划出售旗下子公司，加大页岩气业务的剥离力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/ypf-moves-to-sell-units-as-it-ramps-up-divestments-in-shale-push</link>
